window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After an epic battle in Helmfirth, Nate helped defeat the Adventurer's Guild traitors, free the slaves and save Kiri's lifeâ€”but will it cost him his own?</p> <p>Still navigating his way in this new world, Nate's goal is to learn everything he can and rise up through the levels of the System. To educate himself, he needs to gain access to the Etrua Royal University which will be no easy task, having to compete in a tournament against the most skilled Silver-Ranked Adventurers the Guild has to offer. But the system has other ideas.</p> <p>Will he succeed, or will he be hunted down before he can prove his worth?</p>"; 
